title: Add the location 19,-120 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0x919c0e02cab272b50d0cfa2c70a653ce96f589a6 (Tei)

## Metazone playground

![Metazone playground](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/19/-120/map.png)

Should the scene located at 19,-120 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

This place is a magnifique building. It s totaly usefull, you can buy the nfts, or simply visit, with elevator for go to the different places of the building, even you can go to the underground by an other elevator. Thanks at all

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/en/proposal/?id=cb28e960-cec4-11eb-9861-ebb8fcfd58d2)**
